Name: Lucky Rabbit Reflex!
About the game: An otome (Girl pursues Boy) dating simulation game, Lucky Rabbit Reflex! sees our seventeen-year old heroine beginning her first and final year at a new school. Will she find friendship - or even romance - amongst the motley crew at Northmain College? (Or a decent fashion sense, at the very least!) Game Features: 19 endings 5+ romanceable gentlemen 75 unique CGs 150+ unique items of clothing and accessories CG / endings gallery 178,861 words
